A '''Portage profile''' specifies default values for global and per-package USE flags, specifies default values for most variables found in {{Path|[[:/etc/portage/make.conf]]}}, and defines a [[System_set_(Portage)|set of system packages]]. It masks unstable package versions and USE flags. The profiles are maintained by the Gentoo developers as part of the Gentoo repository ({{Path|[[:/usr/portage/profiles]]}}), but there are ways for users to override single pieces.

